			<div type="transcription">
				<div type="original" xml:lang="yi">
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/11608943/gabersee.html">Gabersee</placeName> Blok N numer 13</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_et_lea_adler">אדלער לאה</persName> 17 יאר אלט. געענדיקט צוויי קלאסן <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1134" type="subject">גימנאזיאלע</term>. געבוֹֹרען אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/687449/zboriv.html"
							>זבוֹרוב</placeName> אין <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">פוֹילן</placeName>. אי אין דער ערשטער צייט פוּן <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-632" type="subject">אקוּפציעס</term> האט מען געמאכט איין <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-346" type="subject">פוֹגרום</term>. נאך דעם <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-346" type="subject">פאגראם</term> איז פוֹרגעקומען איין <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-550" type="subject">אקציא</term>. אין דער אקציא האט מען <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-540" type="subject">אוֹיסגעענדיגט</term> כּימעט די גאנצע שטאט ײִדן. פוּן <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject">קעלט אוּן הוּנגער</term> זענען <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-862" type="subject">גשטורבן</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">מענטשען</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-862" type="subject">מאסנביז</term> [ווייז]. ביים דעם <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-551" type="subject">ליקבידירן דאס געטא</term> בין איך מיט מיינע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">עלטערן</term> אוּן מיין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">ברודער</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">אוֹיסבהאלטן</term> זיך אין <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-567" type="subject">לאגער</term>. ניט הוֹבנדיק 18 יאר האב אין געמוּסט פערלאזן אוּן צעשיידן זיך מיט די
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">עלטערן</term>. <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">אויסבהאלטן</term> האב איך זיך מיט מיינע <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">קרוֹיבים</term> וואס די <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">עלטערן</term> האבן מיך אהינגעשיקט. ארוֹיסגעענדיק פוּן דעם <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">בוּנקער</term> איך דערוווסט זיך דאס מיינע <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">עלטערן</term> נעבען [נעבעך?] <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-745" type="subject">לעבן ניט</term>. ארויס פוּן דעם נקער בין איך דעם 1944 19/VIII.</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_et_lea_adler">אדלער לאה</persName></p>
				</div>
				<div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
					<p><placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/11608943/gabersee.html">Gabersee</placeName> Blok N number 13</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_et_lea_adler">Adler Lea</persName>, seventeen years old. Finished two classes of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1134" type="subject">gymnasium</term>. Born in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/687449/zboriv.html"
							>Zboriv</placeName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798544/republic-of-poland.html">Poland</placeName>. In the first period of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-632" type="subject">occupation</term> they carried out a <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-346" type="subject">pogrom</term>. After the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-346" type="subject">pogrom</term>, there was an <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-550" type="subject">aktion</term>. During the action, they <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-540" type="subject">decimated</term> almost all the Jews of the city. From <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-831" type="subject">cold and hunger</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1207" type="subject">people</term>
						<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-862" type="subject">died en masse</term>. During the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-551" type="subject">liquidation of the ghetto</term>, I, together with my <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">parents</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">brother</term>, <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262"
							type="subject">hid</term> in the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-567" type="subject">camp</term>. Not being eighteen years old, I had to leave and part with my <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject"
							>parents</term>. I <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-262" type="subject">hid</term> with my <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">relatives</term>, to whom my <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">parents</term> sent me. Coming out of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">bunker</term>, I discovered that my <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-822" type="subject">parents</term>, poor things, were <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-745" type="subject">not alive</term>. I left the <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-265" type="subject">bunker</term> on <date when="1944-08-19">August 19, 1944</date>.</p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_et_lea_adler">Adler Lea</persName></p>
				</div>
			</div>
